'''By Hook Or By Crook''' is the fourteenth [[mission]] in Episode 1, [[The Art of War]]. It takes place at the [[Qo'noS]] in the [[Qo'noS (system)|Qo'noS system]].

* Note: To unlock this mission you must choose the [[Augments Faction Center|Augment]] Victory in Episode 1. Otherwise your fourteenth mission will be [[Cleansing Fire]]

